                <fr:title text="Stalk local properties">Stalk local properties</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>
  We say a property of distributive lattices is <html:em>stalk local</html:em>, if for any <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> satisfies <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[P]]></fr:tex> iff for all <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x\in \operatorname {Spec} A]]></fr:tex> in the <fr:link href="/idem-comm-ZAQZ/" title="Prime spectrum of a distributive lattice" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-ZAQZ/" display-uri="idem-comm-ZAQZ" type="local">prime spectrum</fr:link>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A/x]]></fr:tex> satisfies <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[P]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
